0x32C7A7E8C43A1F80.name: ADD_POP_MULTIPLIER_SPHERE
0x32C7A7E8C43A1F80.comment: This native is adding a zone, where you can change density settings. For example, you can add a zone on 0.0, 0.0, 0.0 with radius 900.0 and vehicleMultiplier 0.0, and you will not see any new population vehicle spawned in a radius of 900.0 from 0.0, 0.0, 0.0. Returns the id. You can have only 15 zones at the same time. You can remove zone using REMOVE_POP_MULTIPLIER_SPHERE
